<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is back in the UK after soaking up the sun in St Tropez last month. </p>

<p>And Kimberley Garner showed off her holiday tan as she stepped out for dinner at celeb hotspot Chiltern Firehouse in London on Friday night.</p>

<p>The former Made In Chelsea star, 29, put on a very leggy display in a thigh-skimming cream silk mini dress that was cinched in at the waist with a belt.  </p>

